SETUP INSTRUCTIONS FOR FINA RECOM:

1. Install dependencies:
   pip install spotipy pandas tqdm numpy python-dotenv

2. Set up configuration:
   python config.py
   (This creates .env template - edit with your Spotify credentials)

3. Configure your .env file with:
   - SPOTIPY_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id
   - SPOTIPY_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret
   - SPOTIPY_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:8888/callback

4. Run the system:
   a) Delete existing metadata.json (if any)
   b) python combocode.py (creates user profile metadata.json)
   c) python newmodel.py (starts recommendation engine)

5. Choose your mode:
   - Comfort Zone: Stay close to favorites
   - Balanced Explore: Mix of familiar and discovery  
   - Full Explorer: Maximum discovery

The system will authenticate with Spotify and start playing personalized recommendations!